title: vegan chocolate cake

needs:
 - 1 avocado
 - 150g sugar
 - 175g flour
 - 25g cocoa
 - 200ml unsweetened soya or almond milk
 - 75ml vegetable or sunflower oil
 - 1tsp vanilla extract
 - icing sugar

steps:
 - halve the avocado.
 - cream together half the avocado with the sugar.
 - add the flour, cocoa, milk, oil, and vanilla extract.
 - bake.
 - mix the other avocado half and icing sugar into icing.

notes:
 - http://www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/chocolate-avocado-cake
